<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سعيد بن جُبَير.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣٥١١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو سهل:</span> حسام بن مصك بن<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>سُلْطَان بن ظَالِم.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ابْن بُرَيْدَة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> هشيم، وابو دَاوُد وكناه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>٣٥١٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو سهل:</span> قرط بن حُرَيْث الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أدْرك الشّعبِيّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>سَمِعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>عباسا،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت يحيى بن معِين،<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c5">يَقُول:</span> قرط بن حُرَيْث أَبُو سهل.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٣٥١٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو سهل:</span> حَاتِم بن مَيْمُون<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
