<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مُحَمَّد بن مَرْزُوق وكناه.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٣٥١٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو سهل:</span> بشير، بَصرِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> السّري بن يحيى.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>٣٥١٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو سهل:</span> يحيى بن عُثْمَان<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
